# Roadmap

## Timeline

- **May 20, 2025**
  - Data collection from ESPN and ChampsOrChumps
  - Initial exploration of data structures and quality

- **May 21, 2025**
  - Data cleaning and numeric conversion
  - Scoring function design and team strength computation

- **May 22, 2025**
  - Integrate historical matchup data into model
  - Monte Carlo simulation of 10,000 games
  - Documentation (README, specs, logs, roadmap)

## Deliverables

- Jupyter notebook with full simulation pipeline
- Cleaned Excel data files (`cubs.xlsx`, `white sox.xlsx`, `cubs vs white sox records.xlsx`)
- Project documentation (`Functional_Specs`, `WBS`, `Backlog`, etc.)
- Final win probability outputs and result summary
